restlib

Class ContentInfoBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • restlib.ContentInfoBuilder

  • @NotThreadSafe
public final class ContentInfoBuilder
extends Object
    A builder for generating instances of ContentInfo. ContentInfoBuilder instances can be reused; it is safe to call build() multiple times to build multiple ContentInfo instances.
